---
@META
dir: src/lib
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 13
stack: TypeScript, Prisma 7, NextAuth, Zod, Upstash Redis, swagger-jsdoc

@EXPORTS
prisma.ts: prisma — PrismaClient singleton with pg Pool adapter
auth.ts: authOptions — NextAuth config (Google|GitHub|Credentials providers)
admin-auth.ts: requireAdmin|isAdmin — admin route protection middleware
api-client.ts: APIClient|apiClient|APIError|NetworkError|TimeoutError|safeAPICall|apiRequest — robust fetch client with retry & rate limit handling
api-middleware.ts: applyRateLimit|addRateLimitHeaders|getUserIdFromSession — API rate limiting middleware
cache.ts: CacheService|cache|CacheKeys|CacheInvalidation|cached — Redis caching layer with TTL & stale-while-revalidate
rate-limit.ts: apiLimiter|progressLimiter|xpLimiter|achievementLimiter|authLimiter|getClientIdentifier|checkRateLimit — Upstash rate limiters
gamification.ts: calculateLevel|getXPForLevel|getXPForNextLevel|getProgressToNextLevel|BADGES|checkAchievements|calculateTotalXP|shouldUpdateStreak — XP/level/badge system
achievement-checker.ts: checkAndAwardAchievements — server-side achievement evaluation & DB persistence
glitch-challenges.ts: GlitchChallenge|getRandomChallenge|calculateGlitchReward|shouldTriggerGlitch|getCategoryForLesson|getAllChallenges — cognitive glitch mini-game system
constants.ts: GITHUB_CONFIG|XP_REWARDS|BADGES|GLITCH_CONFIG|LEVEL_CONFIG|COLORS|PAGINATION|RATE_LIMITS|VALIDATION|TIME|LEADERBOARD|XP|BADGE_IDS|ERROR_MESSAGES|SUCCESS_MESSAGES|ROUTES — all app constants
validations.ts: signupSchema|signinSchema|completeChapterSchema|validateRequestBody — Zod API validation schemas (legacy)
validation-schemas.ts: signInSchema|signUpSchema|onboarding*Schema|profileUpdateSchema|completeChapterSchema|answerQuestionSchema|submitTestSchema|submitProjectSchema|createHackathonSchema|createTeamSchema|joinTeamSchema|submitHackathonProjectSchema|updateGraduateProfileSchema|validateAPIRequest|validateQueryParams|formatZodErrors|validateForm — comprehensive Zod validation for all API & form inputs
utils.ts: cn|generateColabUrl — Tailwind class merge utility & Colab URL generator
theme.ts: colors|spacing|borderRadius|shadows|transitions|breakpoints|gradientText|glassEffect|theme — centralized design tokens
env.ts: validateEnv|isRateLimitingEnabled|isSentryEnabled|isOAuthProviderConfigured|env — env var validation with Zod
swagger.ts: swaggerSpec — OpenAPI 3.0 spec generated from JSDoc annotations

@FUNCTIONS
calculateLevel(xp:number) → number
  purpose: compute user level from XP using quadratic formula: floor(sqrt(xp/100))+1
  side-effects: none
  called-by: gamification consumers

checkAndAwardAchievements(userId:string) → Promise<BadgeId[]>
  purpose: evaluate all achievement conditions & persist new badges to DB
  side-effects: db (UserAchievement create, User xp increment)
  called-by: API routes (progress, questions, projects, tests)

applyRateLimit(request:NextRequest, limiter:Ratelimit|null, userId?:string) → Promise<NextResponse|null>
  purpose: check rate limit, return 429 response or null (pass)
  side-effects: api (Upstash Redis)
  called-by: API route handlers

requireAdmin() → Promise<NextResponse|null>
  purpose: verify current user is admin; return error response or null
  side-effects: db (user lookup)
  called-by: admin API routes

validateAPIRequest(request:Request, schema:ZodSchema) → Promise<{success,data}|{success,response}>
  purpose: parse & validate JSON request body against Zod schema
  side-effects: none
  called-by: API routes

@INTERFACES
CacheOptions: { ttl?:number, staleWhileRevalidate?:boolean, serialize?:fn, deserialize?:fn }
GlitchChallenge: { id:string, question:string, options:string[], correct:number, difficulty:enum, category:string, hint?:string, explanation?:string, timeLimit?:number }
Env: Zod-inferred env variable types (DATABASE_URL, NEXTAUTH_*, OAUTH, UPSTASH, SENTRY, NODE_ENV)
SignUpFormData|SignInFormData|ProfileUpdateData|CompleteChapterData|AnswerQuestionData|SubmitTestData|SubmitProjectData|CreateHackathonData|CreateTeamData: Zod-inferred request types

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: @/lib/prisma (cross-ref within lib)
external: @prisma/client, @prisma/adapter-pg, pg, next-auth, @auth/prisma-adapter, bcryptjs, @upstash/ratelimit, @upstash/redis, zod, clsx, tailwind-merge, swagger-jsdoc, dotenv

@STANDARDS
- Two validation files: validations.ts (legacy, simpler) & validation-schemas.ts (comprehensive, preferred)
- Rate limiters gracefully return success:true when Redis not configured
- Cache falls back to direct fetch when Redis unavailable
- All Czech error messages in constants.ts

@WARNINGS
- prisma.ts uses PrismaPg adapter with pg Pool — NOT standard Prisma connection
- Two overlapping validation files — prefer validation-schemas.ts for new code
- constants.ts has BADGES duplicate with gamification.ts BADGES — different keys/structure
- env.ts validateEnv() runs at import time — throws in production if vars missing
---
